Atop the bridge, you can see the heartlands far off into the distance. The body of water here is Lower Peirce Reservoir. These two bodies of water were renamed in 1922 after Robert Peirce, a municipal engineer who implemented the impounding of these reservoirs. https://t.co/A3DdutiLJQ

A dam constructed to look and function like a connecting bridge. On the far right is the Singapore Island Country Club, holding only the more affluent echelons of society, using vast greenery to putt small balls and to the left will be the park, open to the public. https://t.co/9oxCWIHtWS

I didnâ€™t witness it this time around, but yes, there are signages put up to remind park visitors not to feed the monkeys. Compared to the macaques at Bukit Timah, i would say the ones here are more brazen to human presence. Please hang on tight to your bags of food! https://t.co/LQDNPX9APB

The roads here are nicely paved, but this section was gated off, and only â€œAuthorised Vehiclesâ€ were allowed. It made for a calming jog, and quite a serene change from city life. Save for the troops of macaques around! https://t.co/JABU2xpHj3

Day 3 of GRGR, Tour Guide. A photolog of a recovery trot at Upper Peirce. This calm body of water was first impounded back in 1910. As a small island surrounded by saltwater, reservoirs provide a big chunk of freshwater supply to Singapore and its residents. #grgr21 https://t.co/fBh1q0PsIS

Rindu moment moment tu semua . Dulu masa semua sekolah . Kitorang makan luar bila nak sambut birthday je. Itupun kadang sambut pat rumah sebab mak nak masak . Dulu mak rajin buat bubur putih bubur merah tu .

Masatu turn thea yang belanja . Makan sampai 200 lebih tapi ayah makan sikit je. Lepas keluar mall . Thea nak balik rumah sbb masatu kerja melaka . Ayah and mak boleh gi singgah kedai tomyam . Abeh kita tanya nak makan apa suruh kita pilih . Bila kita pilih takmau pulak . Hahaha
Ayah pulak paling tak suka kalau kitorang ajak makan Pizza ke Kenny Rogers ke Boat Noodles. Pernah sekali makan KRR pat Aeon Bandaraya pat Melaka. Dia tak makan pon . Just sentuh ayam sikit .
Dia tak sedar tu yang dia bukan boleh minum manis banyak sangat. Tapi sebab fikir sebulan sekali je kitorang makan luar . So piqa pejam je la mata . Sebab hari hari mak minum susu Glucerna .
Mak paling suka makan pat Kedai tomyam depan bomba . Kalau 10 kali keluar makan . 7 daripada tu dia akan suggest kedai tu. Tak sudah order lai chi kang . Minum sorang je taknak share.
Setiap bulan gilir gilir dengan piqa or DJ untuk belanja makan luar . Tak kisah la makan apa . Janji dalam sebulan tu ada makan luar . Even gi ngeteh mkn roti canai sebelah growth mart tu
Tak tahu kenapa tapi rasa lebih berkat kalau dapat bagi duit belanja untuk mak ayah by hand .
